<a href="http://ec.europa.eu/commission_2010-2014/damanaki/headlines/press-releases/2012/10/201219_en.htm" target="_self">http://ec.europa.eu/commission_2010-2014/damanaki/headlines/press-releas...</a></p><p>Europa Press, ‘Cañete asegura España conseguido “todo” el sector pedia por fondo pesquero’, press release, 24 October 2012</p><p>
